<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Vibe Coding on 知行社</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/tags/vibe-coding/</link><description>Recent content in Vibe Coding on 知行社</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/tags/vibe-coding/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>用AI的人，正在悄悄变笨</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E7%94%A8ai%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E5%8F%98%E7%AC%A8/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E7%94%A8ai%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E5%8F%98%E7%AC%A8/</guid><description>AI帮你写代码、写报告、导航出行，效率翻倍。但有一件事没人告诉你：用久了，那块肌肉会悄悄萎缩。</description></item><item><title>AI帮你到了终点，但路上的风景只能自己看</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%9C%BA%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%9C%BA%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3/</guid><description>Vibe Coding时代，AI能帮你写代码、整理数据、生成方案，但判断力只能自己踩坑练出来。从儿子考试焦虑到程序员白板死磕，说的是同一件事：没走过的路，不算你走过。</description></item></channel></rss>